58:34.261 --> 58:36.763
It sure is.

58:36.805 --> 58:39.641
I wonder how Isla is doing.

58:39.683 --> 58:42.478
You should go and try that shell again.

58:43.395 --> 58:44.271
Yeah.

58:44.313 --> 58:45.856
You never know.

59:09.129 --> 59:11.507
Maybe someday.

59:14.259 --> 59:16.011
I miss you, Isla.

59:16.053 --> 59:19.890
Then it's a good thing
I followed that current.

59:19.931 --> 59:21.308
Isla!

59:21.350 --> 59:22.434
